 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你地係落地簽證定係去領事館簽？</blockquote><br />\n落地 25+8 usd</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落地簽有冇比人收小費？<br />\n除左越南話，當地人講蝗語多定英文多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n機場應該唔會收 越南比起隔離老撾有錢好多 應該都唔會貪污<br />\n當地人講越南文多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但旅遊既人 的士佬 酒店果d講英文多 有d英文仲好過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩年前試過撞過一個越南人講普通話 但佢係因為係澳門珠海打工先識 當地人普遍唔識"},{"pid":"304d36945e0961fd628f3839be23a1d1a54b1d81","tid":180992,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇去浮潛？有冇浮潛公司推介？</blockquote><br />\n絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同男朋友去<br />\n有深潛 即係孭氧氣樽個隻<br />\n冇浮潛<br />\n不過我地係4 island個陣即場比錢join<br />\n唔係跟咩公司<br />\n好似1,200,000越南盾兩個連影相</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1,200,000 會唔會跟埋教練？？<br />\n我女朋友唔識游水玩深潛會唔會有d危險</blockquote><br />\n放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔識游水<br />\n教練係一對一<br />\n基本上淨係識用口呼吸就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係教練游 帶郁你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你地係落地簽證定係去領事館簽？</blockquote><br />\n落地 25+8 usd</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落地簽有冇比人收小費？<br />\n除左越南話，當地人講蝗語多定英文多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇收小費<br />\n英文較多<br />\n有啲普通話都識 但淨係幾句 <br />\n有啲就應該係強國人係到落地生根 流利對話"},{"pid":"406f8c3a233bd3ae18